 services\ndo we want to encrypt and in what way we implement the E2E 
 encryption.\n\nGithub EPIC: 
 https://github.com/SovereignCloudStack/issues/issues/462\nJitsi server on 
 https://conf.scs.koeln:8443/SCS-Tech\nDial-In: 
 +49-221-292772-611\nCoordinator: Filip Dobrovolny 
 <filip.dobrovolny[at]dnation.cloud>
LOCATION:https://conf.scs.koeln:8443/SCS-Tech
DTSTAMP:20250625T073912Z
END:VEVENT
